  <brief_title>The Efficacy and Safety of CARTO 3D Mapping System Versus Conventional Method in AF and VT</brief_title>
  <acronym>CARTOAF&amp;VT</acronym>
  <official_title>Phase â…£ Study of CARTO 3D Mapping System vs Conventional Method in AF &amp; VT</official_title>
